node.text: Uh oh ! I just heard that I can pom pom this weekend liao 😅

Only day 27?!?! U lucky pooch. Mine gives me every 10-14 days!!! 🙄
@chloeshadowminischnauzers Haha.. I always run away when mummy says “shower”! 🙊
@tashi_the_mini_schnauzer haha aiyo why..ask mama use warm water n massage massage u shiok shiok n give treats🤭
@chloeshadowminischnauzers Hmm.. I shower with warm water, but maybe you’re right, I need more sayang and TREATS! Haha 🤣
U seem to enjoy it...ours was earlier...day 25 n 26😅
@shiroboy LOL.. high 🐾!
I showered today too! 💕🐾❤️🚿
@mademoiselle_filou Sure! And thank you for your compliment 🐾
OMG you're adorable 😍 let's be fuRiends 🐾🤗❤️
@maneeonv 😎😎😎
Wow wow wow 🤩
@boscoschnauzer LOL.. another high 🐾!
Me too!
@kaiminischnauzer Haha.. why you 😭! Smells nice nice, good ma, no? 🤣🤣🤣
@tashi_the_mini_schnauzer I don’t like bong bong. I go crazy afterwards. During, sometimes i get mad at hooman and bite her

@kaiminischnauzer Oh dear.. don’t bite mama! 😅 Mama is just trying to keep us clean 🙊 I don’t like to shower but I don’t struggle the moment im in the bathroom 🤣 And guess what, I pee right after my bath - my way of “protesting” 🤭🤭🤭
Me 😭
@janetkk333 Why do the humans like to shower us on Sundays! 😂 Hmm, don’t be fooled by the video, sometimes I growl at mummy when she combs and blow dries me 🙊 Haha 🤣

You do look so fresh & handsome 🤩 YES Sunday is 🛀 day here for both @jacob_ii_mini_schnauzer & @jolie.mini.schnauzer 🛀 Jolie does not lay there enjoying the blow dryer like you 🐶 She HATES the blow dryer 👿👹👿
@gracey.goldendoodle Yes! But the fluffiness won’t last too long.... 🤭
So fluffy after tat! 😍👍🏻
@rileythemini Lol.. you got the wet torture too? 🤣
Not you too 😳🙄😘
@crispycrespi Thank you, I’m always handsome 😎 LOL 🤣🤣🤣
We did! Few days ago. U look handsome now 😘
@navytheschnauzer Mummy loves the fluffy me! 🐾🐾
So fluffy my friend❤️
@elliebeanssss Haha 😂 I roll around anyway, regardless whether I got a bath! 🙊🙊🙊
Me too!! time to roll around more on ALL the furniture 😜🐾
@lil_pumpkin_ho Oh dear.. quickly run and hide! 🤣🤣🤣
Uh oh ! I just heard that I can pom pom this weekend liao 😅
